            <header>
                <h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="name">
                    Is the Dormant Commerce Clause a “Judicial Fraud”?
                    
                                        <meta itemprop="headline" content="Is the Dormant Commerce Clause a “Judicial Fraud”?">
                </h1>
                <div class="published-date">
                    <span class="published-date-label"></span> 
                    <time itemprop="datePublished" content="2015-05-20" datetime="2015-05-20T04:01:32-04:00" class="post-date published">20 May 2015
                    </time>
                    <div class="visuallyhidden">Updated:
                        <time datetime="2015-05-21T17:07:12-04:00" class="updated" itemprop="dateModified">21 May 2015</time>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="author vcard">                 
                    <a href="https://verdict.justia.com/author/dorf" class="url fn author-dorf author-17 post-author-link" rel="author">Michael C. Dorf</a>                </div>
                <div class="featured-image -with-caption" itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject">
